{"tid":2165644,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"財經專題：騰訊阿里敗走美國倒數  近年強攻海外 隨時白費努力","createTime":"2020-08-20T03:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T05:03:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d5e8ea3f275fe023114bc622db7b3d36b4ce7341","tid":2165644,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:19:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200820/PPGKJUMTFNHA7L2Z6FOIC7KAXI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200820%2FPPGKJUMTFNHA7L2Z6FOIC7KAXI%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=92e4d03d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200820%2FPPGKJUMTFNHA7L2Z6FOIC7KAXI%2F&h=450e610d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200820/PPGKJUMTFNHA7L2Z6FOIC7KAXI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n財經專題：騰訊阿里敗走美國倒數 <br />\n近年強攻海外 隨時白費努力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fl7D6pVkT0hakerN62oVDqVRwD4=/2020x1559/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UJZVMNT4CFBQTEEZZEQAAQZBOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ffl7D6pVkT0hakerN62oVDqVRwD4%3D%2F2020x1559%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUJZVMNT4CFBQTEEZZEQAAQZBOE.jpg&h=45324ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■騰訊與阿里若遭美國制裁，恐打擊其全球市佔率。<br />\n<br />\n中美科技戰火舌直逼中國科技巨頭，TikTok母公司字節跳動（Bytedance）成為首當其衝的炮灰；美國總統特朗普揚言騰訊旗下WeChat將成第二打壓目標，阿里巴巴的美國業務相信亦「走唔甩」。面對美國政府來勢洶洶的打壓，市場對騰訊、阿里巴巴等中國科企中長線的海外發展不太樂觀，最壞情況或要完全退出美國市場；而其他與美國關係友好的國家，也可能會跟隨杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：京當年逼微軟交原始碼<br />\n<br />\n中國科技兩大巨頭騰訊及阿里巴巴由於在國內業務逐漸飽和，近年積極拓展海外市場，其中美國成為主要投資基地。本報粗略統計。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n兩間公司近年在海外的發展勢頭一時無兩，其中騰訊開發的網絡遊戲收入更稱霸全球；。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n面對美方打壓，騰訊主席馬化騰為保業績，早前在業績會上反駁兼割席指，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XtVB0JPnKjwpMip0MyszrbtMptg=/886x1072/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QCVWFFGACVFEDPHQYKU477ZHJ4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXtVB0JPnKjwpMip0MyszrbtMptg%3D%2F886x1072%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQCVWFFGACVFEDPHQYKU477ZHJ4.gif&h=b7cb2670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n盈利增長潛力勢降<br />\n<br />\n耀才證券研究部副經理譚智樂指出，微信是通訊軟件，TikTok是「接近並非必需品的社交平台」，兩者業務性質不同；。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n摩根大通發表報告稱，在中美緊張局勢升溫下，中國科企或要對旗下美國業務「大刀闊斧」，「。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yVUs3nnoqCyaF2ETJO31OcZOWH8=/1290x1021/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NEVMQDTRMJFLHHLDHKDUBZCINE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyVUs3nnoqCyaF2ETJO31OcZOWH8%3D%2F1290x1021%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNEVMQDTRMJFLHHLDHKDUBZCINE.gif&h=1db42f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美盟友或加入杯葛<br />\n<br />\n摩通統計，阿里海外市場收入佔總收入約7%，當中美國收入則不多於2%；雖然美國市場現時對阿里來說佔比不算多，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n根據以往中美角力歷史，一旦美國落實封殺令，不排除歐洲、甚至亞洲國家跟隨美國行動，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"8b1b70efeaf5047afa3aeaecc14dbb9839316066","tid":2165644,"uid":291750,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"Yeah yeah yeah"},{"pid":"28632e55337e40fc3aebd4a2a33dd66b320c63e8","tid":2165644,"uid":58209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LA90mBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLA90mBE.jpg&h=4a03b56b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc4580447cd722976fee19c0cf75b6079a449801","tid":2165644,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:22:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"397ce6ddfe4fbf14ffb59f354e7301b5b9b0