-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNEVMQDTRMJFLHHLDHKDUBZCINE.gif&h=1db42f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美盟友或加入杯葛<br />\n<br />\n摩通統計，阿里海外市場收入佔總收入約7%，當中美國收入則不多於2%；雖然美國市場現時對阿里來說佔比不算多，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n根據以往中美角力歷史，一旦美國落實封殺令，不排除歐洲、甚至亞洲國家跟隨美國行動，。。。。。。。。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:31:43.000Z","msg":"幫你推推。<br />\n連登好多人買騰訊，你呢個post應該會無咩人推。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果話制裁匯豐，D人既態度就會好唔同，總之攬炒人地就得，唔好攬炒到我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c8b0dbe56afb71b90418ddb4b9a8a95623ab75","tid":2165644,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"其實單睇樓字冇用架，係人都知大陸盤數係造出嚟去美國上市呃美金，冇咗美國上市條水等於支企身家大縮水，你估支企真係靠企業本身賺錢咩，根本全部都係篤數呃投資者！"},{"pid":"657d5be1c26f9c4f3078ed08dca8609d7cad2981","tid":2165644,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:54:36.000Z","msg":"國外十大遊戲公司 八間騰訊有股份。其他sector 無乜<br />\n<br />\n亞里就東南亞電商同滴滴<br />\n<br />\n佢地D雲係國外都係支那公司用番。"},{"pid":"72e69065290ac8f2042bbd372a5bd9b65c93da10","tid":2165644,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15522136df707c2ec37202c35face031438086a","tid":2165644,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82be1808e40585888f818c98b7f19034fd2b830f","tid":2165644,"uid":58287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5e8ea3f275fe023114bc622db7b3d36b4ce7341","tid":2165644,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:19:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/f